bilingual.target: 它看起来就像一辆汽车。

bilingual.source: This is the worst car in the world.
bilingual.target: 这是世界上最糟糕的汽车。

bilingual.source: The modern car has changed life a great deal.
bilingual.target: 现代汽车极大地改变了生活。

bilingual.source: I think the TV was invented before the car.
bilingual.target: 我认为电视是在汽车之前发明的。

bilingual.source: Well, I think the TV was invented after the car.
bilingual.target: 嗯，我认为电视是在汽车之后发明的。

bilingual.source: Do you think car clubs would be popular in China?
bilingual.target: 你认为汽车俱乐部在中国会受欢迎吗？

bilingual.source: They will have to go somewhere by train or car.
bilingual.target: 他们将不得不坐火车或汽车去某个地方。

bilingual.source: A car is no good to me, since I can't drive.
bilingual.target: 汽车对我没用，因为我不会开车。

list.abstract: 汽车，中国国家最新标准《汽车和挂车类型的术语和定义》（GB/T 3730．1—2001）中的定义为由动力驱动，具有4个或4个以上车轮的非轨道承载的车辆。 汽车主要用于载运人员和（或）货物；牵引载运人员和（或）货物的车辆；特殊用途。1885年10月，德国工程师卡尔·本茨研制成功了世界上第一辆能实际应用的内燃机发动的汽车。1886年，戴姆勒将卧式发动机安装在马车上，创造了第一辆戴姆勒汽车。1913年，美国福特汽车公司推出了全球第一条T型车的组装流水生产线。1978年，日本研制出复合燃料的汽车。汽车体型较小、承载量有限，主要为家庭或私人提供出行便利。 汽车一般由车身、动力总成（发动机、变速箱）、底盘和电子电器装备四个基本部分组成。汽车四大系统是汽车操作系统、汽车动力系统、汽车安全系统、车联网系统。
car是一个外语单词，指小汽车、有轨电车、火车车厢、气球、飞船吊舱、（电梯）升降厢等。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a term that came out of the car industry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这来自于汽车行业。

yingyinNormal.en: Because a car backfired? Okay. Why are you here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 全都是因为汽车放屁？好吧，你来这里干嘛？

yingyinNormal.en: Cleaning the Car!
yingyinNormal.zh: 清洁汽车。

yingyinNormal.en: Cleaning the Car
yingyinNormal.zh: 第1季第49集《清洁汽车》

yingyinNormal.en: Come on car, you can make it. Oh. The car can not drive up the mountain. The snow is too slippery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 加油，汽车，你可以做到。车开不上山了。雪地太滑。

yingyinNormal.en: It was really fun, I mean I've never talked on a car phone before.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真有趣，我从未用过汽车电话。

yingyinNormal.en: One of them could end up in the backseat of her car, or her shower.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以扔一个进她的汽车后座，或是她的浴室。

yingyinNormal.en: I can drive you in the car. No, Daddy. We want to go on the bus. It's fun. Okay, we will go on the bus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以开车带你们去。不用了，爸爸。我们想做公共汽车去，那样很有趣！好吧，我们就坐公共汽车去。

yingyinNormal.en: Books? All right, car magazines, cereal boxes, but it's like enough.
yingyinNormal.zh: 书？好吧，汽车杂志，玉米片包装，但那就够我受的了。

yingyinNormal.en: Welcome to the car of the future. So that's what that button does.
yingyinNormal.zh: 欢迎来到未来汽车系统。啊，所以这个按钮是开启导航的。

yingyinNormal.en: Second one I failed, thanks to you. And the car bomb was insurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 多亏你，我没能杀了第二个人。而汽车炸弹则是最后的杀手锏。

yingyinNormal.en: I understand that your wife has had some car trouble. I wonder how that could have happened?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我听说你妻子的汽车出了故障，那是怎么回事啊？

yingyinNormal.en: Can you believe it? Little Priya's one of the lead attorneys for the biggest car company in India.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们相信吗？小普丽娅是印度最大汽车公司首席律师之一。

yingyinNormal.en: The car is driving itself? Yup. I just put into the GPS the intersection where the crash happened.
yingyinNormal.zh: 汽车会自动行驶？是的，我正让导航把我们带到事故发生的十字路口。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, his rent and car lease are exceedingly high. You couple that with his penchant for dining out and shopping.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他的房租与汽车租贷费用极其高。再加上他喜欢上馆子吃饭与购物。

yingyinNormal.en: When you were little, we moved into this house. We brought all our things on top of our car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当你们还很小的时候，我们搬进这个房子。我们把所有东西装在汽车顶上运过来的。

yingyinNormal.en: What's that sound? Is it a car alarm? Is it a fire-engine? No, it's Baby Alexander.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这到底是什么声音啊？是汽车的警报器响了吗？是不是消防车经过了？不是，是小宝宝亚历山大。

yingyinNormal.en: Coal and car pollutants often produce a permanent twilight in Shanghai, Beijing and other cities.
yingyinNormal.zh: 煤炭与汽车尾气污染物常制造出一种永久的暮色，笼罩于上海、北京和其他城市的上空。

yingyinNormal.en: Objection. Speculation. I'll rephrase. Do you think that the car's capable of erasing its own memory? Yes, I do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 反对，引导证人推测。我换个说法，你觉得汽车有能力清除自身的记忆吗？有。

yingyinNormal.en: And you're in the backseat of your mom's car with your pants off while the whole football team laughs at y...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你光着屁股坐在你妈汽车的后座上时，会有整个橄榄球队队员过来嘲笑你的...

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Many of them have increasing numbers of <highlight>cars</highlight> on the road.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中有许多在路上的汽车越来越多。

examination_example.sentence: They overestimate the potential market of autonomous <highlight>cars</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们高估了自动驾驶汽车的潜在市场。

examination_example.sentence: They present a false picture of the autonomy <highlight>cars</highlight> provide.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们对自动驾驶汽车提供的信息给出了错误的描述。
